---
layout: base.njk
title: Careers
description: "Join Colorado Springs' #1 rated pediatric therapy team. BCBA, OT, PT & SLP careers with medical insurance, 401k, CEU reimbursement, student loan reimbursement & paid time off. 4.8 stars on Indeed."
permalink: /careers/
---

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Join Our Team</h1>
    <p>Make a difference in the lives of children and families every day</p>
    <a href="{{ settings.applyUrl or ('mailto:' + settings.email + '?subject=Career%20Inquiry') }}" {% if settings.applyUrl %}target="_blank" rel="noopener"{% endif %} class="btn-cta page-hero-cta">Apply Now ✉</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Wave: Hero → Content -->
<div class="wave-divider" style="margin-top: -60px; position: relative; z-index: 2;">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 80" preserveAspectRatio="none" style="height:80px;">
    <path d="M0,60 C200,20 400,20 600,40 C800,60 1000,60 1200,20 L1200,80 L0,80 Z" fill="white"/>
  </svg>
</div>

<section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
  <div class="container" style="max-width: 900px;">

    <!-- Employee Satisfaction Highlight — Testimonial Style -->
    <div style="background: #edf2f7; border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.2rem 2rem 1rem; text-align: center; margin: 2rem auto 2.5rem; max-width: 520px; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);">
      <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1a3a5c; line-height: 1.3; margin: 0 0.3rem 0.8rem; font-style: italic;"><span style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 2rem; opacity: 0.5; vertical-align: -0.1em;">&ldquo;</span> We take care of our team the same way we take care of our families. <span style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 2rem; opacity: 0.5; vertical-align: -0.1em;">&rdquo;</span></p>
      <!-- Compact badge with flanking lines -->
      <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0; margin: 0;">
        <div style="flex: 1; height: 1px; background: #c0d0de;"></div>
        <div style="display: inline-flex; align-items: stretch; background: white; border: 2px solid #5eb6d9; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0 0.5rem; transform: scale(0.85);">
          <!-- Left: 4.8 with stars below -->
          <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; padding: 0.4rem 1.2rem; border-right: 1px solid #d0dbe6;">
            <div style="font-size: 1.7rem; font-weight: 800; color: #1a3a5c; line-height: 1;">4.8</div>
            <div style="color: #f5a623; font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-top: 0.2rem;">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
          </div>
          <!-- Right: tagline + buttons -->
          <div style="text-align: left; padding: 0.4rem 0.6rem;">
            <div style="color: #1a3a5c; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.7rem; line-height: 1.25;">#1 Employee Satisfaction<br>in Colorado Springs</div>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.3rem; margin-top: 0.25rem;">
              {% if settings.indeedUrl %}<a href="{{ settings.indeedUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="background: #1a3a5c; color: white; padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;">Indeed</a>{% endif %}
              {% if settings.glassdoorUrl %}<a href="{{ settings.glassdoorUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="background: #0caa41; color: white; padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;">Glassdoor</a>{% endif %}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="flex: 1; height: 1px; background: #c0d0de;"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Why Work With Us?</h2>
    <p>At WellCare & Nurture, we believe in fostering a supportive, multi-disciplinary environment where professionals can grow and make a lasting impact. Our core values guide everything we do — and that starts with how we treat our team.</p>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Benefits</h3>
    <div class="benefits-grid" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
      {% for b in benefits.items %}
      <div class="benefit-item">
        <span class="icon">{{ b.icon }}</span>
        <div>
          <strong>{{ b.name }}</strong>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">{{ b.description }}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <h3 style="margin-top: 2.5rem;">Our Culture</h3>
    <p>We celebrate our team through recognition programs, team-building events, and celebrating work anniversaries and milestones. Our multi-disciplinary collaboration means you'll always be learning from colleagues across specialties.</p>

    <div class="culture-gallery">
      {% for photo in culturePhotos.items %}
      <div class="culture-photo {{ photo.size }}">
        <img src="{{ photo.image }}" alt="{{ photo.caption }}">
        <div class="culture-caption">{{ photo.caption }}</div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2.5rem;">
      <h2>Ready to Make a Difference?</h2>
      <p>We're always looking for passionate, compassionate professionals to join our team.</p>
      <a href="{{ settings.applyUrl or ('mailto:' + settings.email + '?subject=Career%20Inquiry') }}" {% if settings.applyUrl %}target="_blank" rel="noopener"{% endif %} class="btn-cta" style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 1rem;">Apply Now ✉</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
